headline: Why Tyson Foods (TSN) Stock Is Down Today
summary: Shares of meat company Tyson Foods (NYSE:TSN) fell 2.1% in the afternoon session after peer, Hormel, reported disappointing earnings and lowered its financial outlook for the year.
